Package hu.bme.mit.theta.sts.dsl.gen

Class StsDslBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.sts.dsl.gen.StsDslBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
StsDslListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class StsDslBaseListener extends Object implements StsDslListener
This class provides an empty implementation of StsDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
